				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
					<a href="https://github.com/kasturikandalam/osrm-travel-times" 
					   class="hover:text-accent transition-colors" 
					   target="_blank" 
					   rel="noopener noreferrer">
						OSRM Travel Time Tools →
					</a>
				</h3>
				<p class="text-base mb-3 leading-relaxed">
					Lightweight Python tools for computing road-network travel times and distances using the Open Source Routing Machine API. Supports both many-to-many accessibility matrices and pairwise origin-destination calculations—useful for measuring market access, migration costs, and spatial accessibility in development research.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
